title: 03/23/22 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 03/23/22 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Pro Football Focus' Steve Palazzolo about Baker Mayfield's trade value. Can the Browns get anything of value for him? Will Guillory covers the Pelicans for the Athletic and discusses whether he thinks there's a chance we'll see Zion again this season. And Insider Jordan Schultz tells us why he thinks we'll never see Zion in a Pelicans uniform again.
